            "answer_text": "Let the sum be P and rate be x% A = P (1+x/100)^2 = 234 P ( ( 1+x/100)^2)-1) =234\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026(1) A = P ( 1+ x/100)^3 -P = 381 P ( (1+ x/100)^3 -1 ) = 381\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026\u2026.(2) Let ( 1+ x/100) be = a P(a^2\u20131) =234 P ( a^3 -1) = 381 Divide second by 1st ( a^3\u20131) / (a^2\u20131) = 381/234 =1.6282 a= 1.1666 x = 16.67% ANSWER ",
